{"tid":2334090,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"王叔叔被控去年旺角喧嘩辱罵警察 一度被陳慧敏裁定罪成 今高院上訴得直 定罪撤銷","createTime":"2020-12-21T02:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T09:27:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"1034eed9c48b0132f9f6c6e2884c0c2311add4cf","tid":2334090,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12273\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12273&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzHyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=183f635b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12273</a><br />\n#高等法院第一庭<br />\n#黃崇厚法官 #不服定罪上訴<br />\n#1110旺角 #公眾煩擾罪<br />\n<br />\n王(51)(在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序的行為)<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n被告被控於2019年11月10日，在九龍旺角彌敦道與亞皆老街交界，不斷大聲喧嘩及辱罵警察，有理由相信行為會導致現場人士吶喊，擾亂秩序。<br />\n<br />\n背景：<br />\n被告於本年5月28日被時任陳慧敏裁判官裁定罪名成立後，被告不服定罪上訴，被告在本年9月18日第1次就上訴出庭，當時黃崇厚法官要求上訴人及答辯方律師向法庭遞交誓章及理據，並把案件押後至今天再訊。<br />\n<br />\n時任陳慧敏裁判官就本案的裁決理由<br />\n上訴人第一次上庭概要<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n速報：<br />\n上訴得直，定罪撤銷<br />\n<br />\n律政司不會申請重審案件"},{"pid":"b204ad6b4653d31f869571ce0458d68f172c55c5","tid":2334090,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T02:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e847cf2241b146a90d51a2f119b8f8f34c3b8516","tid":2334090,"uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T02:44:28.000Z","msg":"今朝兩單案算判得正常😂😭😭😭"},{"pid":"1f3963458381716a2f8c489214caa63bba4c735e","tid":2334090,"uid":5312,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTim